Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:03.85,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}inochi no shuchou to muimi no shoumei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:10.53,op romaj,,0,0,0,,anata ni wa taikutsu shinogi ni taranu kokkei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:15.73,op romaj,,0,0,0,,shihaisha kidori no oroka na shuzoku wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:21.67,op romaj,,0,0,0,,unuboreta chisetsu na teiri wo narabeta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.76,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{"M}mugen{"} to shinjita ai mo sora no kanata mo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:33.62,op romaj,,0,0,0,,bokutachi ni shimesareta kasou no jiyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:39.69,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{"Y}yuugen{"} sore wa mujihi ni toki wo kizami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:44.14,op romaj,,0,0,0,,asu sae mo hitei suru sentaku e
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.70,op romaj,,0,0,0,,Hacking to the Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:53.54,op romaj,,0,0,0,,ikutsu mono kagayakeru hibi nakama to no yakusoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:58.54,op romaj,,0,0,0,,nakatta koto ni wa shite wa ikenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:05.48,op romaj,,0,0,0,,sono tame ni toki wo azamuku nokosareta shikake ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:11.75,op romaj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}mou mayoi wa nai kodoku no kansokusha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:03.85,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Mesmo que os pontos de vista da vida e suas provas sem sentido
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:10.53,op trans,,0,0,0,,não sejam nada para você e não possam aliviar seu tédio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:15.73,op trans,,0,0,0,,As pessoas tolas daquela raça, atuando como líderes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:21.67,op trans,,0,0,0,,têm escrito teoremas infantis que fedem à vaidade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.76,op trans,,0,0,0,,Temos tido a liberdade de imaginar as coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:33.62,op trans,,0,0,0,,como o amor infinito que está além do céu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:39.69,op trans,,0,0,0,,A crueldade finita permite que o tempo flua
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.69,0:02:44.14,op trans,,0,0,0,,assim dirijo minha escolha para renunciar o amanhã
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.70,op trans,,0,0,0,,Hackeando o Portão
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:53.54,op trans,,0,0,0,,Eu não deveria fingir que não fiz promessas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:58.54,op trans,,0,0,0,,para voltar com meus amigos para aqueles dias vividos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:05.48,op trans,,0,0,0,,Então agora iludirei o próprio tempo com os truques que me restam,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:11.75,op trans,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}assim como sou um observador solitário sem mais dúvida alguma
